"""
        Test that the inequality operator returns True when comparing two
        QueryResponsePayload structures with different client registration
        methods fields.
        """
a = payloads.QueryResponsePayload(client_registration_methods=[enums.
    ClientRegistrationMethod.CLIENT_GENERATED, enums.
    ClientRegistrationMethod.CLIENT_REGISTERED])
b = payloads.QueryResponsePayload(client_registration_methods=[enums.
    ClientRegistrationMethod.CLIENT_GENERATED])
self.assertTrue(a != b)
self.assertTrue(b != a)
